t
c = 525-\dfrac 34t
4 c = 2100 - 3t \iff c = \dfrac {2100}{4} - \dfrac {3t}{4} \iff 525 -\dfrac 34 t
5\;\left(\underbrace{525 - \frac 34 t}_{\large = \;c}\right) + 2t = 1750
